ding on the exact jet definition. To\nour knowledge SMEFT effects of this type have so far not been discussed in the\nliterature. The presented MC generator can also serve as a starting point to\nobtain NNLO$+$PS accuracy for a suitable enlarged set of effective operators in\nthe future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2022 19:01:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2022 16:19:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-11"}
