 R&D to be able to deliver and maintain the targeted luminosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2022 21:36:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2022 09:10:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-07"}
